  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my grandfather and my brother and I slept downstairs in a room.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the middle of the night-- actually, not in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to sleep early because it was a curfew and we couldn't light any candles or light inside.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One thing, we didn't have any, probably.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two, we didn't want to attract anybody from the outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it must have been late at night, and it was very dark.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I heard German officers right across the street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a Ukrainian family living there, and they had young girls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the officers, they were sitting outside and laughing and talking to those girls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somehow they managed to communicate between the German and the Ukrainian because most Ukrainians didn't speak German.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And suddenly I hear the German voices approaching close to the house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then suddenly I see a flash light shining inside the house on the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were, like, looking to see maybe there was something open in the attic, going up to an attic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they walked around to the side where the door was and they started knocking on the door and yelling [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was my grandfather's name, and for some reason they knew the name, which tells me that the neighbors, you know, told them what the name was, and that the neighbors may have told them that-- because the Ukrainians kept score.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew who was captured already and who was taken away already, you know, so they knew that they haven't-- this was already a day or two after they started this particular sort of action against Jews, where now they were going to the homes and they were-- they were taking Jews out and they were taking them away and shooting them.",
      "word_count": 62
    }
  ],
